gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 132, Lakers 127
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Lakers in overtime, 132-127. De'Aaron Fox led all scorers with 37 points and eight assists for the Kings, while Malik Monk added 22 points in the victory. Anthony Davis (30 points, 16 rebounds, three blocks) and LeBron James (27 points, 15 rebounds, eight assists) combined for 57 points for the Lakers in the losing effort. The Kings improve to 2-1 on the season, while the Lakers fall to 1-2.
